		<description><![CDATA[<p>TOGETHER BUILDING A BETTER COMMUNITY. Thursday Sept 19 2014  Canceled &#160; &#160; If you did not join us for the June  Repair café then you should definitely make a point to come to this one! We will rescheduled in OCT/NOV time so keep your broken stuff.   Also, you may try repairpdx.org for other times and &#8230; <a href="http://northportlandtoollibrary.org/events/repair-cafe-2/" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="screen-reader-text">Repair Cafe Sept 2014</span> <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>
